GIS1

Class MyGisElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • GIS1.MyGisElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GIS_element

    public class MyGisElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements GIS_element
    This class represents a GIS element with geometric representation and meta data such as: Orientation, color, string, timing... THIS class works with gps coords: x - long y - lat z - alt
    Author:
    Naor and michael

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      Point3D p
      The object variables p- point3d with gps/geo/lat-long style coords color data - location of this point (for example :Israel/jerusalem) UTC - the utc time-zone of this point timing- the date and time of the element creation d- metaData object description.
